p1: This is a 'simplified' version of the CivitAI website. The main purpose of this page was to create a way to search models on CivitAI without dealing with the original site's terrible performance.
Due to limitations of the public API from CivitAI, many features available on the original site are missing here.
It's sad that the API doesn't provide information about articles (list and content) üò≠
(You can switch the language in the page footer)
home.autoplayDescription: If autoplay is disabled, cards won‚Äôt show GIFs, and videos on all pages will be paused by default, only playing on hover.
home.resizeDescription: If SW resizing is enabled, images on the card page will be resized to their actual size (with DPR in mind) before being displayed. Otherwise, the server-provided size will be shown with automatic scaling.
home.resizeNote: For example: the server returned an image sized 320x411 for a 300x450 request ‚Äî with SW resizing enabled, the page will still get 300x450, and the browser won't need to resize it on the fly.
home.cachesDescription: This is information about the disk cache size used by this site. If you changed DPR (page/interface scaling), or the SW resizing setting, there may be outdated image sizes left. They will be cleaned up automatically over time, but you can also clear them manually.

temp.articles: CivitAI's public API does not provide a list or content of articles üò¢
